doc_summary_long: A 34-year-old man froze to death after the ran from the scene of a car crash, officials said. Mark Henderson was involved in a collision near 97th Street and Good Hope Road around 2:15 Saturday morning, CBS 58 reports. Police said Henderson ran from the scene and officers could not immediately locate him.
doc_summary_short: A 34-year-old man froze to death after the ran from the scene of a car crash, officials said.
doc_title: Man freezes to death while hiding from police, report says
